const FACTS = ["Mandarin has no verb tenses — 吃 (eat) stays 吃 whether it happened yesterday, now, or tomorrow. Time words and particles do the work.","Traditional characters often hide meaning clues: 好 (good) is 女 (woman) + 子 (child).","Every Chinese syllable carries a tone — mā 媽 (mother) and mǎ 馬 (horse) differ only in tone.","Zhuyin (ㄅㄆㄇㄈ) is the phonetic system taught in Taiwan — 37 symbols, learned before characters.","Chinese counts nouns with a measure word: 一本書 (a book), 一張票 (a ticket), 一杯咖啡 (a cup of coffee)."];

window.DATA = { CATEGORIES, WORDS, FACTS };
